#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn29:11.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso sāratthiko sāragavesī sārapariyesanaṃ caramāno "
"mahato rukkhassa tiṭṭhato sāravato atikkammeva sāraṃ phegguṃ chetvā ādāya "
"pakkameyya ‘sāran’ti maññamāno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:11.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ cakkhumā puriso disvā evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:11.3"
msgid ""
"‘na vatāyaṃ bhavaṃ puriso aññāsi sāraṃ na aññāsi phegguṃ na aññāsi tacaṃ na "
"aññāsi papaṭikaṃ na aññāsi sākhāpalāsaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:11.4"
msgid ""
"Tathā hayaṃ bhavaṃ puriso sāratthiko sāragavesī sārapariyesanaṃ caramāno "
"mahato rukkhassa tiṭṭhato sāravato atikkammeva sāraṃ phegguṃ chetvā ādāya "
"pakkanto “sāran”ti maññamāno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:11.5"
msgid "Yañcassa sārena sārakaraṇīyaṃ tañcassa atthaṃ nānubhavissatī’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.196"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn29:12.1"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, idhekacco kulaputto saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ "
"pabbajito hoti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.2"
msgid ""
"‘otiṇṇomhi jātiyā jarāya maraṇena sokehi paridevehi dukkhehi domanassehi "
"upāyāsehi, dukkhotiṇṇo dukkhapareto, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.3"
msgid ""
"appeva nāma imassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa antakiriyā paññāyethā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.4"
msgid "So evaṃ pabbajito samāno lābhasakkārasilokaṃ abhinibbatteti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.5"
msgid "So tena lābhasakkārasilokena na attamano hoti na paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.6"
msgid "So tena lābhasakkārasilokena na attānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.7"
msgid ""
"So tena lābhasakkārasilokena na majjati nappamajjati na pamādaṃ āpajjati, "
"appamatto samāno sīlasampadaṃ ārādheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.8"
msgid "So tāya sīlasampadāya attamano hoti, no ca kho paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.9"
msgid "So tāya sīlasampadāya na attānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.10"
msgid ""
"So tāya sīlasampadāya na majjati nappamajjati na pamādaṃ āpajjati, appamatto "
"samāno samādhisampadaṃ ārādheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.11"
msgid "So tāya samādhisampadāya attamano hoti, no ca kho paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.12"
msgid "So tāya samādhisampadāya na attānukkaṃseti, na paraṃ vambheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.13"
msgid ""
"So tāya samādhisampadāya na majjati nappamajjati na pamādaṃ āpajjati, "
"appamatto samāno ñāṇadassanaṃ ārādheti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.14"
msgid "So tena ñāṇadassanena attamano hoti paripuṇṇasaṅkappo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.15"
msgid "So tena ñāṇadassanena attānukkaṃseti, paraṃ vambheti:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.16"
msgid ""
"‘ahamasmi jānaṃ passaṃ viharāmi, ime panaññe bhikkhū ajānaṃ apassaṃ "
"viharantī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.17"
msgid ""
"So tena ñāṇadassanena majjati pamajjati pamādaṃ āpajjati, pamatto samāno "
"dukkhaṃ viharati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.18"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, bhikkhu phegguṃ aggahesi brahmacariyassa;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn29:12.19"
msgid "tena ca vosānaṃ āpādi."
msgstr ""

